@DominicFarrell This has got me thinking. I think it’s a (deliberate?) misunderstanding that FBPE, “lefties” etc don’t WANT to be proud of the UK.
We absolutely 100% DO want to be proud of it. 
We just wish the government (and the “far right”) would give us something we can be proud of.

