@CCWearmouth @DrRJWebb Also depends on whether your local setup has PED as part of ED, part of paeds, or a standalone entity.
In most trusts, PED is part of ED and @clifford0584 would have an ED ST4+ level doc on hand for support.
In others he might have paeds reg as his “senior”. 1/2

