@K_G_Spearpoint @katemasters67 Have. The. Conversation. 

Frame it well - as part of a bigger discussion about prognosis and “what we will do”, not just “what we won’t do”.

Ask yourself realistically what CPR/ITU etc would look like for the patient in front of you and what the outcome would be.

